author: Slidebean
description:
Why OpenAI’s $100B raise marks a new phase of AI financing.

OpenAI’s reported fundraising ambitions far exceed the limits of traditional venture capital.
By courting sovereign wealth funds, the company is positioning itself not as a startup but as foundational infrastructure.

The scale, timing, and valuation suggest a shift:
AI development is no longer just a tech investment.
It’s becoming a strategic, nation level asset.

title: OpenAI wants to raise $100B in one round and that’s the least wild part
